Create Virtual Machine screen shot 

# vim-cmd vmsvc/getallvms

The snapshot related commands that the vmsvc/ namespace has available are:

snapshot.create
snapshot.dumpoption
snapshot.get
snapshot.remove
snapshot.removeall
snapshot.revert
snapshot.setoption
get.snapshotinfo


Example ::::

# vim-cmd vmsvc/snapshot.create 10 test


where 10 is VM ID and "TEST" is the name of backup 



++++++++++++++Backup VMDK File+++++++++++


# vmkfstools -i /vmfs/volumes/Storage1/examplevm/examplevm.vmdk /vmfs/volumes/Storage2/examplevm_clone.vmdk